   This manual is a derivative work created for educational and operational 
   purposes. It is based on official documentation for GnuPG (GPG), YubiKey 
   (Yubico), and standard Linux utilities. Users are advised to verify 
   commands against the official vendor documentation for their specific 
   versions.

